|Betis]]\n|[[2017\u201318 Real Betis season|2017\u201318]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|La Liga\n|29||2||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||30||2\n|-\n|[[2018\u201319 Real Betis season|2018\u201319]]\n|31||0||6||0||5||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||42||0\n|-\n|[[2019\u201320 Real Betis season|2019\u201320]]\n|20||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||22||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!80||2||9||0||5||0||0||0||94||2\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!410||36||21||1||37||1||2||0||470||38\n|}\n\n===International===\n{{updated|7 July 2019}}<ref name=\"NFT\">{{NFT|13043}}</ref><ref name=\"RSSSF\"/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|colspan=\"3\"|[[Mexico national football team|Mexico]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|2005||1||0\n|-\n|2006||7||0\n|-\n|2007||18||3\n|-\n|2008||10||3\n|-\n|2009||9||1\n|-\n|2010||14||1\n|-\n|2011||15||5\n|-\n|2012||10||1\n|-\n|2013||12||0\n|-\n|2014||13||1\n|-\n|2015||13||7\n|-\n|2016||10||2\n|-\n|2017||10||1\n|-\n|2018||7||0\n|-\n|2019||9||3\n|-\n!Total||158||28\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n{{updated|19 June 2019}} (scores and results list Mexico's goal tally first)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/jose-andres-guardado-hernandez/425/matches/|title=A. Guardado \u2013 Matches|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=14 October 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"NFT\"/>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!Goal!!Date!!Venue!!Opponent!!Score!!Result!!Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 27 February 2007 || [[Qualcomm Stadium]], [[San Diego]], United States || {{fb|VEN}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20131 || [[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 2. || 24 June 2007 || [[Soldier Field]], [[Chicago]], United States || {{fb|USA}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 1\u20132 || [[2007 CONCACAF Gold Cup]]\n|-\n| 3. || 14 July 2007 || [[Estadio Ol\u00edmpico (Caracas)|Estadio Ol\u00edmpico]], [[Caracas]], [[Venezuela]] || {{fb|URU}} || align=center | '''