es || {{fb|GUY}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 5\u20130 || [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification \u2013 CONCACAF Third Round|2014 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 15. || 23 June 2014 || [[Itaipava Arena Pernambuco]], [[S\u00e3o Louren\u00e7o da Mata]], Brazil || {{fb|CRO}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20131 || [[2014 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n| 16. || 9 July 2015 || Soldier Field, Chicago, United States || {{fb|CUB}} || align=center | '''4'''\u20130 || align=center | 6\u20130 || rowspan=6|[[2015 CONCACAF Gold Cup]]\n|-\n| 17. || 15 July 2015 || [[Bank of America Stadium]], [[Charlotte, North Carolina|Charlotte]], United States || {{fb|TRI}} || align=center | '''3'''\u20133 || align=center | 4\u20134\n|-\n| 18. || 19 July 2015 || [[MetLife Stadium]], [[East Rutherford, New Jersey|East Rutherford]], United States || {{fb|CRC}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 1\u20130\n|-\n| 19. || rowspan=\"2\" | 22 July 2015 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Georgia Dome]], [[Atlanta]], United States || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|PAN}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"|2\u20131\n|-\n| 20. || align=center | '''2'''\u20131\n|-\n| 21. || 26 July 2015 || [[Lincoln Financial Field]], [[Philadelphia]], United States || {{fb|JAM}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20131\n|-\n| 22. || 13 November 2015 || rowspan=\"2\"|Estadio Azteca, Mexico City, Mexico || {{fb|SLV}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\"|[[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification \u2013 CONCACAF Fourth Round|2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 23. || 29 March 2016 || {{fb|CAN}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20130\n|-\n| 24. || 28 May 2016 || Georgia Dome, Atlanta, United States || {{fb|PAR}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 1\u20130 || rowspan=\"3\"|Friendly\n|-\n| 25. || 10 November 2017 || [[King Baudouin Stadium]], [[Brussels]], Belgium || {{fb|BEL}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20131 || align=center | 3\u20133\n|-\n| 26. || 5 June 2019 || [[Mercedes-Benz Stadium]], Atlanta, United States || {{fb|VEN}} || align=center | '''3'''\u20131 || align=center | 3\u20131\n|-\n| 27. || rowspan=\"2\" | 19 June 2019 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Broncos Stadium at Mile High]], [[Denver]], United States || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|CAN}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"| 3\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[2019 CONCACAF Gold Cup]]\n|-\n| 28. || align=center | '''3'''\u20131\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n===Club===\n'''Deportivo'''\n*[[Segunda Divisi\u00f3n]]: [[2011\u201312 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n|2011\u201312]]\n*[[UEFA Intertoto Cup]]: [[2008 UEFA Intertoto Cup|2008]]\n\n'''PSV'''\n*[[Eredivisie]]: [[2014\u201315 Eredivisie|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 Eredivisie|2015\u201316]]\n*[[Johan Cruyff Shield]]: [[2015 Johan Cruijff Schaal|2015]], [[2016 Johan Cruyff Shield|2016]]\n\n===International===\n'''Mexico'''\n*[[CONCACAF Gold Cup]]: [[2011 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2011]], [[2015 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2015]], [[2019 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2019]]\n*[[CONCACAF Cup]]: [[2015 CONCACAF Cup|2015]]\n\n===Individual===\n*[[Liga MX|Mexican Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] Rookie of the Tournament: [[2005 Primera Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico Apertura|Apertura 2005]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mediotiempo.com/futbol/liga-mx/entrega-balon-oro-apertura-2005-clausura-2006-expo-futbol|title=Se entrega El Bal\u00f3n de Oro del Apertura 2005 y Clausura 2006 en la Expo Futbol|trans-title=Golden Ball award for Apertura 2005 and Clausura 2006 at Expo Futbol|publisher=Medio Tiempo|language=Spanish|date=25 July 2006|accessdate=14 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Liga MX|Mexican Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] Full-back of the Tournament: [[Primera Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico Apertura 2006|Apertura 2006]],<ref name=\"Oro\">{{cite web|url=https://espndeportes.espn.com/noticias/nota?s=mex&id=585023&type=story|title=Estrellas de oro|trans-title=Golden sta